source: crates/audiomirror-cli/tests/help_snapshots.rs
expression: output
---
Start the AudioMirror background daemon (signaling server + device watcher).

Example: audiomirror-cli daemon --signaling-port 5100

Usage: audiomirror-cli daemon [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --signaling-port <SIGNALING_PORT>
          [default: 7000]

      --peer-name <PEER_NAME>
          

      --identity-dir <IDENTITY_DIR>
          

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
